comments.en:
(ssg_17.txt from 東方幻想的音楽)
 This song is very different from the previous one, and I tried to put out the atmosphere of the mini-orchestra.
It aims to be an orchestra in a very narrow hall or a narrow place like a clubhouse.

Marisa's theme already hits the fourth song, but for the first time it became a villainish song this time. Well, you're a villain. (^^;
Furthermore, from witch to witch. (^^;

The point of reflection is that the song is not very shooting game-like. (sort of)
I was focused on the atmosphere.
For now, if you only look at the song, isn't it cool? (^^;

Anyway, it's a short song (^^;

